{"tid":1236173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個網好似教人Delete TVB台","createTime":"2019-06-17T11:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T04:49:55.000Z","uid":252296,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7f337906d78321d64857394481c55e29938b8b54","tid":1236173,"uid":252296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2016/02/23/hkppl-remove-j5-guide/top-news/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Funwire.hk%2F2016%2F02%2F23%2Fhkppl-remove-j5-guide%2Ftop-news%2Famp%2F&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCo%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=5857c942\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/unwire.hk/2016/02/23/hkppl-remove-j5-guide/top-news/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">事不疑遲！<br />\nDel佢老母！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ecacb627c19dc53279f79fef2abc55e52ba96ae3","tid":1236173,"uid":252296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"30e23538d6d930ac37da2924ce1963a11e6eae9d","tid":1236173,"uid":252296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"51fb5e5b6b4cbe7d702dd7f56ed71d4b00d3afcd","tid":1236173,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a7d98038663154d8201466f29efc65830fccb2","tid":1236173,"uid":157938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=yUf3ZniyPWjB5eI%2FQURZCo%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=17184206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"d3df5f5fe3e22a583ddbb42bd43f7e6fd9eb57c6","tid":1236173,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:32:44.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"f982915fb559e757779f751c8f5c889cddaa5ce4","tid":1236173,"uid":252296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:49:55.000Z","msg":"push"}]}